       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COB06250.
      ******************************************************************
      *                                                                *
      *     Processa registos de vencimentos da VIA                    *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
      * Descriçăo da funcionalidade                                    *
      * - Actualiza registos com erro de factura năo encontrada        *
      ******************************************************************
      *           L O G     D E     A L T E R A C O E S                *
      ******************************************************************
      *  INICIO  * AUTOR  * FIM    *  C O M E N T A R I O S            *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
      *
      ******************************************************************
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3001 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6702 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD8205 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME              PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COB06250'.
           05 CON-COVT6702             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT6702'.
           05 CON-COVT6405             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT6405'.
           05 CON-COVT8205             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT8205'.
           05 CON-COVT3001             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT3001'.
           05 CON-CS-2                 PIC  X(01) VALUE '2'.
           05 CON-S                    PIC  X(01) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-CR                   PIC  X(02) VALUE 'CR'.
           05 CON-DATE-MIN             PIC  X(10) VALUE '0001-01-01'.
      ********* CONTAS **************
           05 CON-CTA-VENCIMENTO        PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA01001'   .
           05 CON-CTA-SEGSOC-CB         PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA13001'   .
           05 CON-CTA-IRS               PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA13002'   .
           05 CON-CTA-SEGSOC-EP         PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA06001'   .
           05 CON-SUBS-FERIAS           PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA01002'   .
           05 CON-SUBS-NATAL            PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA01003'   .
      ********* STATUS **************
           05 CON-TRANSMIT              PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'TR'.
           05 CON-INTEGRADO             PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'IN'.
           05 CON-RECEBIDO              PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'RC'.
           05 CON-ERRO                  PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'ER'.
           05 CON-PROCESSADO            PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'PR'.
      ********* ERROS ***************
           05 CON-ERR-PER-MULT          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '001'.
           05 CON-ERR-IDFOR-NOTFND      PIC  X(03)  VALUE '002'.
           05 CON-ERR-IDFOR-MULT        PIC  X(03)  VALUE '003'.
           05 CON-ERR-IDINV-NOTFND      PIC  X(03)  VALUE '004'.
           05 CON-ERR-AMOUNT-INV        PIC  X(03)  VALUE '005'.
           05 CON-ERR-STAT-INV          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '006'.
           05 CON-ERR-VALOR-INV         PIC  X(03)  VALUE '007'.
           05 CON-ERR-MULT-INV          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '008'.
           05 CON-ERR-MARG-INV          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '009'.
           05 CON-ERR-STAT-PAG          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '010'.
      ********* STATUS DATA *********
           05 CON-ACTIVO                PIC  X(01)  VALUE 'A'.

      ********* MARGEM **************
           05 WS-VALOR-MAX     PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-VALOR-MIN     PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-MARGEM        PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-PERCENT       PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
      *

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DATA-SEARCH            PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-MINIMA            PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE              PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NSEQ                   PIC S9(10)  COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.

           05 WS-ANO-PER-WRK               PIC  9(04).
           05 WS-MES-PER-WRK               PIC  9(02).

           05 WS-ANO-SS                    PIC  X(04).
           05 WS-MES-SS                    PIC  X(02).
      ******************************************************************
      *  SWITCH
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-SWITCHES.
           05 WS-STATUS-COT82       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT82-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT82-NOTFND               VALUE 100.

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCL0001.
           COPY AQCW0109.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIAW0011.
           COPY VIAW0012.
           COPY VIATK001.
           COPY VIATK002.
           COPY COCK0002.
           COPY COCK0001.
           COPY COCF3100.
           COPY VIAL1000.
           COPY COCL0250.
           COPY COCL0255.

      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.

      *
      * MOVIMENTOS BANCARIOS A CREDITO
      *
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE COT82 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT
                         IDFICH
                       , DINTEGR
                       , DPAG
                       , CREF
                       , MVALOR
                       , DRECB
                       , DEXEC
                       , CSTATUS
                       , CUSERID
                       , HTIMEST
                       , CIDEMP
                       , CPERIOD
                       , NIDPROJECTO
                       , NIDINVOICE
                       , CERRO
                       , NTOTALAMOUNT
                       , CTIPO
                       , CSUBTIPO
                       , MVLRTOT
                       , MVLROTH
                       , ICONTAB
                 FROM COVT8205
                 WHERE  CSTATUS  = "ER"
                   AND  ICONTAB  = "S"
                   AND  CERRO    = "004"
                   AND  MVLRTOT <> 0
                   AND  NIDINVOICE = 0
                 ORDER BY CPERIOD, IDFICH, CIDEMP, NIDPROJECTO,
                          CTIPO DESC, CSUBTIPO
           END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE'.
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCW0009.
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING AQCW0009-DATA.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
      ******************************************************************
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-INICIO
                 THRU AQCP0100-REG-INICIO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ
                 THRU AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-OPEN-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT

              PERFORM 2400-PROC-CURSOR
                 THRU 2400-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT
                      UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                         OR NOT AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   CLOSE COT82
              END-EXEC
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2200-OPEN-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2200-OPEN-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD8205.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN COT82
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT8205        TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2200-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2300-FETCH-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2300-FETCH-CURSOR'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH  COT82
               INTO
                    :COCD8205-IDFICH
                  , :COCD8205-DINTEGR
                  , :COCD8205-DPAG
                  , :COCD8205-CREF
                  , :COCD8205-MVALOR
                  , :COCD8205-DRECB
                  , :COCD8205-DEXEC
                  , :COCD8205-CSTATUS
                  , :COCD8205-CUSERID
                  , :COCD8205-HTIMEST
                  , :COCD8205-CIDEMP
                  , :COCD8205-CPERIOD
                  , :COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO
                  , :COCD8205-NIDINVOICE
                  , :COCD8205-CERRO
                  , :COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD8205-CTIPO
                  , :COCD8205-CSUBTIPO
                  , :COCD8205-MVLRTOT
                  , :COCD8205-MVLROTH
                  , :COCD8205-ICONTAB
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT8205        TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2400-PROC-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2400-PROC-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC
                 THRU 2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD8205-NIDINVOICE EQUAL ZEROES
               PERFORM 2500-OBT-INVOICE
                  THRU 2500-OBT-INVOICE-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
      **R    IF COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO AND
             IF (COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                 COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB) AND
                 COCD8205-NIDINVOICE NOT EQUAL ZEROES
               MOVE SPACES                 TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
               MOVE SPACES                 TO COCD8205-CERRO
               PERFORM 2695-TENTA-MARGEM
                  THRU 2695-TENTA-MARGEM-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD8205-NIDINVOICE NOT EQUAL ZEROES
               PERFORM 2500-UPD-INVOICE
                  THRU 2500-UPD-INVOICE-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
      **R    IF COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO AND
             IF (COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                 COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB) AND
                 COCD8205-NIDINVOICE NOT EQUAL ZEROES
               PERFORM 2510-TRATA-PAG
                  THRU 2510-TRATA-PAG-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2400-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-OBT-INVOICE.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-OBT-INVOICE'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD6702           REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                 ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES


           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
           MOVE COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
           MOVE COCD8205-CIDEMP        TO COCD6702-GCLIENTE

           MOVE COCD8205-DPAG(1:4)       TO WS-ANO-PER-WRK
           MOVE COCD8205-DPAG(6:2)       TO WS-MES-PER-WRK

           MOVE WS-ANO-PER-WRK           TO WS-ANO-SS
           MOVE WS-MES-PER-WRK           TO WS-MES-SS

           IF (COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-NATAL OR
               COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-FER)   AND
             (COCD8205-CSUBTIPO = COCK0002-SEG-SOC-EMP OR
              COCD8205-CSUBTIPO = COCK0002-SEG-SOC-FUNC)
             IF COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-NATAL
               MOVE 'SSSN'                 TO COCD6702-GREFINV
             END-IF
             IF COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-FER
               MOVE 'SSSF'                 TO COCD6702-GREFINV
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF (COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-NATAL OR
               COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-FER)   AND
             (COCD8205-CSUBTIPO = COCK0002-VAL-IRS)
             IF COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-NATAL
               MOVE 'IRSN'                 TO COCD6702-GREFINV
             END-IF
             IF COCD8205-CTIPO = COCK0002-SUBS-FER
               MOVE 'IRSF'                 TO COCD6702-GREFINV
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  NIDINVOICE
                     ,  NTOTALAMOUNT
                     ,  CSTATUS
                  INTO :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6702-CSTATUS
                  FROM  COVT6702_EXPENSES
                 WHERE GCLIENTE          = :COCD6702-GCLIENTE
                   AND NIDPROJECTO       = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND YEAR(DDATAEMISS)  = :WS-ANO-SS
                   AND MONTH(DDATAEMISS) = :WS-MES-SS
                   AND CSTATUS          <> "04"
                   AND GREFINV           = :COCD6702-GREFINV
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6702           TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
             IF (COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                 COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB)
               MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE     TO COCD8205-NIDINVOICE
               MOVE CON-INTEGRADO           TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
               MOVE SPACES                  TO COCD8205-CERRO
             END-IF
             IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-PAG
               MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE     TO COCD8205-NIDINVOICE
               MOVE CON-ERRO                TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
               MOVE CON-ERR-STAT-PAG        TO COCD8205-CERRO
             END-IF
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD8205-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
           WHEN DB2-DUPLINE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD8205-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE CON-ERRO                  TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERR-MULT-INV          TO COCD8205-CERRO
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE

                MOVE COCD6702-GCLIENTE      TO AQCW0100-DESC1(1:)
                MOVE COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO   TO AQCW0100-DESC1(4:)
                MOVE COCD6702-GREFINV       TO AQCW0100-DESC1(13:)

                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-OBT-INVOICE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-UPD-INVOICE.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-UPD-INVOICE'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO COCD8205-CUSERID

           IF COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT NOT EQUAL ZEROES AND
              COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT EQUAL ZEROES
             MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT8205
                   SET CSTATUS      = :COCD8205-CSTATUS
                     , CERRO        = :COCD8205-CERRO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT = :COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NIDINVOICE   = :COCD8205-NIDINVOICE
                     , CUSERID      = :COCD8205-CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST      = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
                 WHERE IDFICH      = :COCD8205-IDFICH
                   AND CIDEMP      = :COCD8205-CIDEMP
                   AND CPERIOD     = :COCD8205-CPERIOD
                   AND NIDPROJECTO = :COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND CTIPO       = :COCD8205-CTIPO
                   AND CSUBTIPO    = :COCD8205-CSUBTIPO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT8205               TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-UPD-INVOICE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2510-TRATA-PAG.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2510-TRATA-PAG'           TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
      **R    IF COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO AND
             IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM
               PERFORM 2695-RECEBIMENTO
                  THRU 2695-RECEBIMENTO-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO AND
                COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB
               PERFORM 2700-PAGAMENTO
                  THRU 2700-PAGAMENTO-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2510-TRATA-PAG-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2695-RECEBIMENTO.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2695-RECEBIMENTO    '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             SET  COCL0255-NORMAL         TO TRUE
             MOVE COCD8205-CIDEMP         TO COCL0255-GCLIENTE
             MOVE COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO    TO COCL0255-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE COCD8205-NIDINVOICE     TO COCL0255-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE COCD8205-MVLRTOT        TO COCL0255-MVALOR
             IF COCL0255-MVALOR < 0
               COMPUTE COCL0255-MVALOR = COCL0255-MVALOR * -1
             END-IF
             MOVE COCD3001-DPAG           TO COCL0255-DDATEDUE
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCD8205-CSTATUS = CON-INTEGRADO
           AND COCD8205-CERRO = SPACES
           AND COCD8205-ICONTAB = 'S'

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-INIT
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-INIT-EXIT

             PERFORM COCP0255-CALL-ROTINA
                THRU COCP0255-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-END
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-END-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
               MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
               MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
               PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                  THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCD8205-CSTATUS = CON-INTEGRADO
           AND COCD8205-CERRO = SPACES
           AND COCD8205-ICONTAB = 'S'
             MOVE CON-RECEBIDO               TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCD8205-CERRO
             MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB      TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
             MOVE ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO     TO COCD8205-DRECB
             MOVE COCD8205-DPAG              TO COCD8205-DPAG
             PERFORM 2650-UPD-STATUS
                THRU 2650-UPD-STATUS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2695-RECEBIMENTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2700-PAGAMENTO.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2700-PAGAMENTO      '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             MOVE COCD8205-NIDINVOICE     TO COCL0250-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE COCD8205-CIDEMP         TO COCL0250-GCLIENTE
             MOVE COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO    TO COCL0250-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE COCD8205-MVLRTOT        TO COCL0250-MVALOR
             IF COCL0250-MVALOR < 0
               COMPUTE COCL0250-MVALOR = COCL0250-MVALOR * -1
             END-IF
             MOVE COCD3001-DPAG           TO COCL0250-DPAG
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCD8205-CSTATUS = CON-RECEBIDO
           AND COCD8205-CERRO = SPACES
           AND COCD8205-ICONTAB = 'S'
           AND (COCD3001-DPAG = ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO
            OR  COCD3001-DPAG < ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO)
           AND COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-INIT
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-INIT-EXIT

             PERFORM COCP0250-CALL-ROTINA
                THRU COCP0250-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-END
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-END-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
               MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
               MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
               PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                  THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCD8205-CSTATUS = CON-RECEBIDO
           AND COCD8205-CERRO = SPACES
           AND COCD8205-ICONTAB = 'S'
           AND (COCD3001-DPAG = ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO
            OR  COCD3001-DPAG < ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO)
           AND COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO
             MOVE CON-PROCESSADO             TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCD8205-CERRO
             MOVE ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO     TO COCD8205-DEXEC
             MOVE COCD8205-DRECB             TO COCD8205-DRECB
             MOVE COCD3001-DPAG              TO COCD8205-DPAG
             PERFORM 2650-UPD-STATUS
                THRU 2650-UPD-STATUS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2700-PAGAMENTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2650-UPD-STATUS.
      ******************************************************************

           MOVE '2650-UPD-STATUS     '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO COCD8205-CUSERID

           IF COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT NOT EQUAL ZEROES AND
              COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT EQUAL ZEROES
             MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT8205
                   SET CSTATUS      = :COCD8205-CSTATUS
                     , CERRO        = :COCD8205-CERRO
                     , DRECB        = :COCD8205-DRECB
                     , DPAG         = :COCD8205-DPAG
                     , DEXEC        = :COCD8205-DEXEC
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT = :COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , CUSERID      = :COCD8205-CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST      = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
                 WHERE IDFICH      = :COCD8205-IDFICH
                   AND CIDEMP      = :COCD8205-CIDEMP
                   AND CPERIOD     = :COCD8205-CPERIOD
                   AND NIDPROJECTO = :COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND CTIPO       = :COCD8205-CTIPO
                   AND CSUBTIPO    = :COCD8205-CSUBTIPO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT8205               TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2650-UPD-STATUS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           MOVE COCD8205-CPERIOD           TO COCD3001-CPERIOD
           MOVE COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO       TO COCD3001-NIDPROJECTO

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT DPAG
                     , ISTATUS
                  INTO :COCD3001-DPAG
                     , :COCD3001-ISTATUS
                  FROM COVT3001_PARMVENC
                 WHERE CPERIOD     = :COCD3001-CPERIOD
                   AND NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3001-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3001               TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2695-TENTA-MARGEM.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2695-TENTA-MARGEM  '    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCD8205-CSUBTIPO = COCK0002-VAL-IRS
             MOVE 0,4                        TO WS-PERCENT
           ELSE
             MOVE 0,2                        TO WS-PERCENT
           END-IF.

           COMPUTE WS-MARGEM  = COCD8205-MVLRTOT *
                            WS-PERCENT.

           COMPUTE WS-VALOR-MAX  = COCD8205-MVLRTOT +
                                   WS-MARGEM.

           COMPUTE WS-VALOR-MIN  = COCD8205-MVLRTOT -
                                   WS-MARGEM.

           IF WS-VALOR-MAX < 0
             COMPUTE WS-VALOR-MAX = WS-VALOR-MAX * -1
           END-IF

           IF WS-VALOR-MIN < 0
             COMPUTE WS-VALOR-MIN = WS-VALOR-MIN * -1
           END-IF

           IF COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT > WS-VALOR-MAX
           OR COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT < WS-VALOR-MIN
              MOVE CON-ERRO                TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
              MOVE CON-ERR-MARG-INV        TO COCD8205-CERRO
           ELSE
              MOVE CON-INTEGRADO           TO COCD8205-CSTATUS
              MOVE SPACES                  TO COCD8205-CERRO
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2695-TENTA-MARGEM-EXIT  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCD8205-CIDEMP      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  COCD8205-CIDEMP        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  COCD8205-NIDPROJECTO   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  COCD8205-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'WS-VALOR-MAX     '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (4)
              MOVE  WS-VALOR-MAX           TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE 'WS-VALOR-MIN     '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (5)
              MOVE  WS-VALOR-MIN           TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
              MOVE 'COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (6)
              MOVE  COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
              MOVE 'COCD8205-MVLRTOT     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (7)
              MOVE  COCD8205-MVLRTOT       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(7)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2695-TENTA-MARGEM-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '3000-FIM-PROGRAMA'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Processos finais
            PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
               THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

            PERFORM AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT
               THRU AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT-EXIT.

           PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-FIM
              THRU AQCP0100-REG-FIM-EXIT.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE AQCP0002 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCP0009.
           COPY AQCP0109.
           COPY VIAP0012.
           COPY VIAP0015.
           COPY VIAP1000.
           COPY COCP0250.
           COPY COCP0255.
      ******************************************************************
